preference.name: MEDefaultExportTransferOptionSet
preference.preference_description:
Specifies the list of valid transfer option set values in "Export to Briefcase" dialog's transfer option set dropdown. The values shown in the transfer option set dropdown are dependent on: 1. Values in this preference 2. Values of transfer mode in preference "TC_gms_export_default_transfermode".
With value of preference "TC_gms_export_default_transfermode" as "TIEExportDefaultTM" there will be two cases: 1. Only those transfer option set will be displayed in "Export to Briefcase" dialog's transfer option set dropdown that are specified in this preference and have transfer mode value as "TIEExportDefaultTM". 2. All the transfer option set with transfer mode value as "TIEExportDefaultTM" will be displayed in "Export to Briefcase" dialog's transfer option set dropdown, if none of the transfer option set names specified in this preference have transfer mode value as "TIEExportDefaultTM".
Default values for the dropdown are: * MfgConfiguredExportDefault_LL: Use this transfer option set for briefcase configured LowLevel export. * MfgConfiguredExportDefault: Use this transfer option set for briefcase configured export. * MfgUnconfiguredExportDefault: Use this transfer option set for briefcase unconfigured export. The first value specified in this preference defaults to selected transfer option set on the export to briefcase dialog.
